title: The Trailer Of Anushka Sharma’s ‘Phillauri’ Is SO Good
text:
Rashmi Daryanani Feb . 6 . 2017 
Phillauri marks Anushka Sharma ‘s second venture as a producer (her first was NH10 ), and it’s a project that she’s acting in as well. The trailer has just been released online, and I’m bowled over by how good it looks. Such an interesting concept– absolutely love! 
The film stars Anushka, Suraj Sharma, Diljit Dosanjh and Anshai Lal and will release on March 24th. SO excited for this! 20
